## Limitations
The search results provided limited information specifically on Black ethnicities and their predisposition to diabetes. Further research is needed to explore the socio-economic and genetic factors affecting Black populations. Additionally, the data primarily focused on South Asians within the broader category of South East Asians, which may not fully represent the diversity within this group.